These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There 4 different types of food: pear, grapefruit, spinach, plum
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, gardening, hiking, sudoku
1. the person eating grapefruit is between the person eating pear and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
3. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere between the person eating plum and the person eating pear##7
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
5. the person eating plum is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Food   | spinach | plum       | grapefruit | pear        |
| Hobby      | hiking  | gardening | sudoku        | board-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, hedgehog, snake
There 4 different types of food: avocado, potato, eggplant, asparagus
1. the person eating asparagus is somewhere between the person eating eggplant and the owner of the hedgehog##7
2. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
3. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the right of the person eating asparagus##5
4. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
5. the person eating asparagus is between the person eating eggplant and the person eating potato##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | hedgehog | goat       | snake         | dog     |
| Food   | potato   | asparagus | eggplant | avocado |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, mystery, scientific
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, lilac, light-blue, blood-red
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
2. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere between the person who likes lilac and the person who likes turquise##7
3. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person who likes turquise is somewhere between the person who likes blood-red and the person watching crime movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | scientific | mystery | comedy  |
| Color   | light-blue | turquise  | blood-red   | lilac |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, monopoly, canasta, billiard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, golf, skateboarding, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person playing backgammon is somewhere between the person who's sport is golf and the person playing billiard##7
3. the person playing canasta is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Game   | monopoly | backgammon | billiard       | canasta |
| Sport   | golf      | climbing   | skateboarding | volleyball  |

