.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
House: victorian, gothic-revival, cottage, craftsman
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, chinese, german
1. the german is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
2. the american is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5
3. the victorian house is on the right of the cottage house##1
4. the german is somewhere between the gothic-revival house and the victorian house##7
5. the german is on the left of the chinese##1
6. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the german##5
7. the gothic-revival house is on the far left or far right##3
8. the victorian house is on the left or right of the cottage house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| House         | cottage | victorian   | craftsman | gothic-revival |
| Nationality   | american      | brazilian | german      | chinese |

