.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, colombian, spanish
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, tulip, iris, lily
1. the argentine is not the person who growslily##6
2. the person who growsiris is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
3. the spanish is the person who growsiris##1
4. the colombian is somewhere between the spanish and the american##7
5. the argentine is on the left of the american##1
6. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
7. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | spanish | colombian | argentine | american |
| Flower           | iris   | lily    | daffodil       | tulip  |

