.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, satire, thriller, western
City: san-francisco, edinburgh, london, berlin
1. the person watching western movies is somewhere between the person watching family movies and the person traveling to berlin##7
2. the person watching satire movies is not the person traveling to london##6
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is not the person watching thriller movies##6
4. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to berlin##5
5. the person watching family movies is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
6. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | western | satire | thriller |
| City           | san-francisco    | edinburgh   | berlin  | london      |

