.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, soy-milk, 7up, coffee
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, rock, soul, trance
1. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the fan of gospel##5
2. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
3. the fan of rock is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking soy-milk and the fan of rock##2
6. the fan of soul is somewhere between the fan of rock and the person drinking soy-milk##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Beverage   | coffee | sprite | soy-milk | 7up   |
| Music-Genre   | rock    | soul      | gospel      | trance |

