3. the swisher-smoker is not the person who's hobby is writing##6
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
5. the prince-smoker is somewhere to the right of the chaman-smoker##5
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who's hobby is puzzles##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |    4    |
