.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, filmmaking, fishing, hiking
House: futuristic, wooden, tower, ranch-style
1. the wooden house is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the futuristic house##1
3. the tower house is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is not the wooden house##6
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the wooden house##1
6. the wooden house is somewhere between the futuristic house and the person who's hobby is fishing##7
7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the tower house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby       | hiking | collecting | filmmaking | fishing |
| House   | futuristic   | ranch-style      | wooden        | tower  |

