3. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
4. the fan of house is in an even position##4
5. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the fan of hip-hop##5
6. the owner of the bird is on the left of the fan of house##1
7. the owner of the goat is the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Pet      | bird   | cat | goat | horse   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | house   | indie | hip-hop |

