3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
4. the person traveling to miami is somewhere between the person traveling to new-york and the fan of metal##7
5. the fan of reggae is somewhere between the fan of salsa and the person traveling to liverpool##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3     |   4    |
| City           | liverpool | edinburgh | miami | new-york  |
| Music-Genre   | metal     | reggae   | salsa    | techno |

