.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
House: ranch-style, craftsman, farmhouse, wooden
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, quad-bike, scooter
1. the farmhouse house is somewhere between the person driving the bus and the craftsman house##7
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the wooden house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the farmhouse house##5
5. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| House         | craftsman    | farmhouse | wooden     | ranch-style |
| Transport   | quad-bike | scooter  | motorbike | bus |

 